{"tid":1535244,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣228事件的失蹤人口和太子站的音訊全無","createTime":"2019-09-03T09:41:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T17:36:38.000Z","uid":281401,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"02b0c76fe839e2271e4a740d4a536781e317f3e1","tid":1535244,"uid":281401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:41:32.000Z","msg":"太子站男子毫無音訊，讓我想起台灣228事件，國軍登台逮捕與鎮壓殺害台灣民眾。<br />\n當中許多亡者均有名有姓，但也不乏所謂的「失蹤」，連屍體也找不到，估計是槍殺後屍體直接扔到海裡。<br />\n<br />\n直到現在，228已平反，事件已塵封在博物館裡，可那些人仍然是「失蹤」，沒有人知道他們是誰。<br />\n<br />\n原來即使後來平反，亡者不一定可以沉冤得雪，他們死得不明不白。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人一定要堅持落去，唔好比呢件事係歷史洪流中被掩蓋。</span>"},{"pid":"6d269e938fd6f59be89c384153dc746dcf228f10","tid":1535244,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:41:37.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"89a5ea1a64c7e8f46074b749443a69773a9cb832","tid":1535244,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:42:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/